<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=634244" target="_blank">My Saddlebags</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kullgendphlith>Kullgen dPhlith</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://home.comcast.net/~subacca/spin.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>NOT A MAN</span><br>  Posts: 790<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/22/03 8:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4066.topic&index=18>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://home.comcast.net/~subacca/come_here.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: &quot;i'm a little short for a trade&quot;</span><hr size=1> Oh, well, then. Let me set the scene <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Picture it - Highkeep, 3129 (or whatever damned year it was 3 months ago)... <br>
<br>
Evariel and I are finally the same rank (after not only my, but her reroll as well) and we decide to head to HHK. Now, I'd never hunted there in all of my EQ life, but we'd been there for a few days, and I felt marginally comfortable. We manage to get the  ... um, main room? Not the warrior room, or the raider room - the one right off the stairs. Anyway, wonder of wonders, we even have a dark group, and a friend on the way for that 6th spot. We're all doing great, even with me doing the tap/siphon heal shuffle for my tanking wife, and we even derailed a few trains. <br>
<br>
Here comes Mithrell. <br>
<br>
He butts his way in - in the MIDDLE of a fight - and spams &quot;grp plz&quot; repeatedly. I'm not talking once or twice, but outdoing the battlespam, even. After we manage to get through the battle, he starts with the &quot;WTF GRP PLZ&quot; business. I explain that we have someone coming for the 6th spot, but he doesn't take no for an answer. &quot;Im a pal I can heal u&quot; he says. Well, that would have booted him even if he hadn't been a rude git. I repeat, sorry - no room.<br>
<br>
He disappears. <br>
<br>
When he returns 2 minutes later, he has all of the RR and WR on his ass. He shouts TRAIN after he does about 5 laps around us, making sure to run over my medding, 1/4life ass on each turn about. However, between well-timed roots and excellent fighting, we live. <br>
<br>
Mithrell insists he warned us, etc ... but when I ask why he did laps rather than zone, he says nothing but &quot;grp plz&quot;. This time I let him know that even IF the spot wasn't already claimed, he wouldnt be welcome because he's a pally, etc etc. He disappears this time after a &quot;WTF bitch&quot;. <br>
<br>
I'm used to that by now. No biggie. <br>
<br>
It's quiet for about 5 minutes this time before we hear other people in the zone shouting about a &quot;guard train&quot; and mentioning Mithrell's name. Yep, that's right. That fuckwit gathered all the guards he could and ran down to the basement to dump them on our KOS group. Everyone but me (&lt;3 feign) dies.<br>
<br>
I am pissed. I send him rather pointed (and likely reportable <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :o --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/embarassed.gif ALT=":o"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ) tells, and he stands over my feigned body, nearly dead and oom, and challenges me to a duel. Oh, did I mention he was above my rank? Yeah, but he still had to wait until I was almost dead. I get up, regen and med to full, and accept. He runs. That was the most disappointing moment of my life, honestly. Pallys, especially asshole d00d pallys, are my favorite kills! &lt;sigh&gt; <br>
<br>
Rezes and heals, regroup and move to the WR. He returned about 3 more times to train us before shouting that he needed a port out. Well, this was an opportunity not to be missed. A friend in the group, who shall remain nameless <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> , had access to a rather high level wizard character and logged him posthaste. <br>
<br>
Mithrell spent the night in CT. <br>
<br>
Now, I'm not honestly a bitchy, mean woman in real life, but whenever I see a corpse of his I beam. So, I am not surprised to find that he's also a begging piece of shit on top of a coward. I hate that jackass, and anyone that has any dealings with him has my utmost sympathy.<br>
<br>
